Package edu.ucdenver.tournament

Class Tournament

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucdenver.tournament.Tournament
  • public class Tournament
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Tournament consists of lists that keep track of countries,players,teams,matches, and referees this includes methods for adding to each of these lists and acts as the main functionality of the program contains functionality for loading and saving the program to a file as well as retrieving lists to find matches with parameters
